
# 🎬 Netflix Landing Page Clone

A Netflix-inspired landing page clone built using HTML and CSS.

## 🚀 Features

- Responsive Hero Section
- Netflix Style UI
- Language Selector
- Sign In Button
- Background Overlay Effect
- Clean Layout using Flexbox

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Flexbox

